Download TauDEM 5.1.2 C++ source files from http://hydrology.usu.edu/taudem/taudem5/

Copy shape directory into src from TauDEM 5.2 obtained from GitHUB repository. Build the files inside this directory.

Uninstal openmpi-common and install mpich2.

Add #include <stdio.h> to linearpart.h and areadinfmn.cpp.

Download and unzip shapelib into src folder. Rename the extracted folder to shape.  Build shapelib.

Add to SHAPEFILE entry of makefile the following  shapelib/shpopen.o shapelib/safileio.o
